channel.title: Help, My Shop Keeps Walking Away
channel.description: Hello, Im a beginner coder and it's going good..till 1 of my shops KEEPS WALKING AWAY !! Please anyone help ? the other ones didnt and its the same shop.

item.title: Help, My Shop Keeps Walking Away
item.dc:creator: @katr0x katr0x_
item.description:
@katr0x wrote:

An autospawn.cfg is made like this:
//------NpcID—CoordX–CoordY–Height–RangeX1-RangeY1-RangeX2-RangeY2-WalkType-Description

Under the names it will have the numbers.
Replace the numbers under the RangeX1 till RangeY2 with 0 to make them stop walking at all, or other coords to make them walk different.

Read full topic
